  "title": "Foot Reflexologists / Masseurs Wanted",
  "description": "<h3><u><strong>Highlights</strong></u></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Great ambience and working environment</li>\n  <li>High Commision Scheme</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><u><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></u></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Massages customers with body lotion or rubbing oil.</li>\n  <li>Massages body using techniques such as rubbing, stroking flesh or kneading to stimulate blood circulation, relaxation of contracted muscles, facilitate elimination of waste matter or to relieve other conditions using hands.</li>\n  <li>Assist and direct clients in activities such as reduing or remedial exercises.</li>\n  <li>Uphold hygiene standards and follow health and safety regulations.</li>\n  <li>Cooperate with and report on administration on any arising issues.</li>\n  <li>Ad-hoc work instructed by store supervisor.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Preferrably has 2 or more years of foot reflexology/massage experience</li>\n  <li>Able to work shifts, e.g. 10am to 6pm or 12pm to 8pm</li>\n  <li>Able to start work as soon as possible</li>\n</ul>",
